---
import VerticalPage from '../../layouts/VerticalPage.astro';
import Section from '../../components/layout/Section.astro';
import SectionHeader from '../../components/layout/SectionHeader.astro';
---

<!-- Industry Statistics Sources:
  - DHS CISA: Government facilities are among the 16 critical infrastructure sectors designated by Presidential Policy Directive 21
  - Federal Protective Service (FPS): Protects 9,000+ federal facilities; reports thousands of security incidents annually
  - GAO: Federal facility security spending exceeds $2 billion annually
  - Buy American Act (41 USC 8301-8305): Requires federal agencies to prefer American-made goods in procurement
  - Trade Agreements Act (19 USC 2501): Governs procurement of products from designated countries
  - GSA Schedule: Federal procurement vehicle for pre-approved vendors
  - NIST SP 800-53: Security and Privacy Controls for Federal Information Systems
  - Executive Order 14017 (2021): America's Supply Chains, emphasizing domestic manufacturing
-->

