  <!-- Government Trust Signals Section -->
  <Section class="bg-slate-950">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <SectionHeader
        title="Built for Government Trust"
        subtitle="Credentials and capabilities that meet the highest standards"
      />
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">
            <img src="/icons/us-flag.svg" alt="American Flag" width="48" height="32" class="inline-block" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Buy American Act Ready</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">In-house manufacturing at our Holly Hill, Florida facility provides full domestic origin documentation. Our hardware meets Buy American Act procurement requirements for federal acquisitions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4"><svg class="w-8 h-8 text-igt-cyan" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Federal LE Background</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Senior leadership with 28 years of federal law enforcement experience including ICE, U.S. Border Patrol (Employee of the Year 2000), and FLETC instructor credentials. We understand government security from the inside.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4"><svg class="w-8 h-8 text-igt-cyan" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8 21h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-2H10v2a2 2 0 1 1-4 0V5a2 2 0 1 0-4 0v3h4"/><path d="M19 17V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H4"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">11 Security Patents</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Proprietary technology protected by 11 patents in security systems. Our solutions are engineered from the ground up, not assembled from off-the-shelf components and rebranded.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Government Use Cases -->
  <Section>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <SectionHeader
        title="Serving Every Level of Government"
        subtitle="Security solutions for federal, state, and local facilities"
      />
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Federal Facilities</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Office buildings, courthouses, and service centers require security that meets NIST, FISMA, and agency-specific standards. American-manufactured hardware with on-premise data storage supports federal compliance mandates. Our leadership's DHS background means we speak the language of federal security operations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">State and Local Government</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">City halls, county offices, public works facilities, and community centers serve the public while managing access and protecting staff. Portable SecMod units provide cost-effective coverage for facilities that cannot justify permanent enterprise installations. Competitive pricing works within municipal budget cycles.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Law Enforcement and Public Safety</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Police stations, evidence storage facilities, and public safety operations centers require restricted access and continuous monitoring. Tiered access control, autonomous patrol units, and AI threat detection provide layered protection for sensitive law enforcement environments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Critical Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Water treatment plants, power substations, and transportation hubs require perimeter security in remote locations with limited infrastructure. Solar-powered, cellular-connected SecMods provide autonomous monitoring without facility modifications or network dependencies.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</VerticalPage>
